  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Linguistics              : Exploration of the development of prosodic and segmental structure in children, with an emphasis on current theoretically-informed work in this area.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              This course is not scheduled for the 2014-2015 academic year.          </p>

